{"tid":2143632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人行報告：包商銀行將被申請破產","createTime":"2020-08-07T08:06:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T11:38:30.000Z","uid":26770,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c02a27c03e7b6505e25102768a01605f606b2b67","tid":2143632,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:06:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542275-20200806.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542275-20200806.htm&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLKd04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=2bc71b7a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542275-20200806.htm&h=70767dec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542275-20200806.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人民銀行表示，根據前期包商銀行嚴重資不抵債的清產核資結果，包商銀行將被申請破產，有關部門正依法依規對相關人員追責問責。<br />\n<br />\n人行發布第2季度貨幣政策執行報告，並以專欄形式首次披露包商銀行處置情況，表示為保障包商銀行流動性安全，接管以來人行在接受足額優質抵押品前提下，向包商銀行提供235億元人民幣額度常備借貸便利流動性支持，不僅高於2004年證券公司綜合治理時期的保障程度，與國際上同類型機構風險處置時的債權保障程度相比，亦是比較高的水平。<br />\n<br />\n貨幣政策執行報告又提到，高風險中小金融機構處置順利實施，積極化解部分城市商業銀行、農村商業銀行、農村信用社多年隱藏的風險，最大程度保護債權人合法權益。推動省級政府「一省一策」制定中小金融機構風險處置規劃。錦州銀行、恒豐銀行改革重組方案順利實施。<br />\n<br />\n人行在5月時提到，因疫情影響，包商銀行後續依法處置工作進度需適當延後，接管期限延長6個月，直至今年11月23日。"},{"pid":"ecc2e2e4ab57b9d5bf8ed699f3892822cb31ba91","tid":2143632,"uid":284432,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:07:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a72732b74411b293351c83ba16c2d3d9a4ddfe0a","tid":2143632,"uid":137493,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:08:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"de29be2e1173fa71cbc4e51605aedcf69e5a3d6f","tid":2143632,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:18:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ca2baaa1723495a93fe537174fa1b54b86fee3","tid":2143632,"uid":47259,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:24:27.000Z","msg":"無陰功, 共咗呢間仲爭5千億USD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf48024520c74e9d74a8e641b386091e9b388cb4","tid":2143632,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:43:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b95b3ebe9a222c5bf52a4b1cf715174ba720a5f8","tid":2143632,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T11:19:01.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3dfccb9d8e60f8aae435ae21cf566c2d149e7c0","tid":2143632,"uid":5490,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T11:27:32.000Z","msg":"托少日騰訊都救到佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95903295bcc74c1d5b6970c60e9cc1b0622df501","tid":2143632,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3dfccb9d8e60f8aae435ae21cf566c2d149e7c0","tid":2143632,"uid":5490,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T11:27:32.000Z","msg":"托少日騰訊都救到佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T11:38:22.000Z","msg":"明天系銀行"},{"pid":"683b93cdd59cb21d499bee4ad0fb4919e0734242","tid":2143632,"uid":167597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3dfccb9d8e60f8aae435ae21cf566c2d149e7c0","tid":2143632,"uid":5490,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T11:27:32.000Z","msg":"托少日騰訊都救到佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T11:38